{"title":"西财摄记 | 整个夏天想和你环游世界","uid":"a93e87b2f48eb84fe192d269e2ab9b32","slug":"推文7","date":"2021-07-31T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T15:38:55.639Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文7.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230912870.png","content":"<p>“夏风停在耳边，</p>\n<p>嘱咐你要热爱这个世界。”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230912870.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230912870\"></p>\n<p>在20级的军训生活尾声</p>\n<p>本来该计划着出游拍照的我们</p>\n<p>却又被疫情困在了温江</p>\n<p>“那就骑小电驴去学校附近的鲁家滩呗”</p>\n<p>“好耶好耶”</p>\n<p>“想拍jk！”</p>\n<p>“好！！”</p>\n<p>“嘻嘻嘻”</p>\n<p>于是,骑上小电驴兜着风 </p>\n<p>开着蓝牙音箱哼着歌 </p>\n<p>我们的夏日假期就宣告开始咯</p>\n<p> <img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303230959703.png\" alt=\"image-20220303230959703\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231003697.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231003697\"></p>\n<p>当时很幸运</p>\n<p>天空是一望无际的蓝色 </p>\n<p>白云是软绵绵的糖果 </p>\n<p>树林是光影斑驳的温柔</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231013764.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231013764\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231017914.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231017914\"></p>\n<p>在鲁家滩</p>\n<p>寻得见能映出远山与朝霞的小河</p>\n<p>找到了日系电影一样浪漫的柏油路</p>\n<p>还有 麦色的小木屋 </p>\n<p>和阳光下闪烁温暖的鹅卵石岸</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231029766.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231029766\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231038577.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231038577\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231041951.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231041951\"></p>\n<p>拍累了</p>\n<p>一人抱着一杯冰镇水果茶</p>\n<p>坐在树荫下的小电驴上</p>\n<p>暖风黏糊糊地吹在身上</p>\n<p>听知了不停地为夏天续曲 </p>\n<p>看太阳逐渐向西落下</p>\n<p> 云朵被染成嫩嫩的粉红</p>\n<p>“好浪漫啊”</p>\n<p> <img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231102974.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231102974\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231109135.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231109135\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231115721.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231115721\"></p>\n<p>离开鲁家滩的时候</p>\n<p> 我在盛夏里许了愿 </p>\n<p> 希望疫情快快过去 </p>\n<p>希望华夏岁岁平安</p>\n<p>因为 整个夏天还想和你 </p>\n<p>环游世界</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231127470.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231127470\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231131686.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231131686\"></p>\n<p>祝愿从这个夏日开始 </p>\n<p>大家都能成为自己心上人的</p>\n<p>四季限定</p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>感谢</summary>\n<p>摄|钟志涛</p>\n<p>出镜|赵思宇</p>\n\n</details>\n","text":"“夏风停在耳边， 嘱咐你要热爱这个世界。” 在20级的军训生活尾声 本来该计划着出游拍照的我们 却又被疫情困在了温江 “那就骑小电驴去学校附近的鲁家滩呗” “好耶好耶” “想拍jk！” “好！！” “嘻嘻嘻” 于是,骑上小电驴兜着风 开着蓝牙音箱哼着歌 我们的夏日假期就宣告开始咯...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":445,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财摄记","slug":"西财摄记","count":9,"path":"api/categories/西财摄记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"夏","slug":"夏","count":6,"path":"api/tags/夏.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Swufe了吗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/deelsilcon/pics/raw/master/uPic/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"分享生活，记录美好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"weichat":{"icon":"/img/wechat.png","link":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303234741533.png"},"mail":{"icon":"/img/mail.png","link":"mailto:271215314@qq.com"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"西财摄记 ｜ 拥抱最后的夏天","uid":"86deda4bc8055be095eccdd3214944c8","slug":"推文8","date":"2021-09-26T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T15:38:50.856Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文8.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231455106.png","text":"“我仍记得， 夏日橘子汽水的心动。” 你在夏天会喝汽水吗？ 拉开易拉罐的拉环 气泡混合着清新的甜味喷薄而出 就像一声忍俊不禁的轻笑 裹挟着夏日的喜悦 一瓶橘子味的汽水 足以将我拉回整个灿烂的夏天 九月中旬 风歇雨停 似乎能听见黄桷兰滑下枝头 坠入夏末傍晚 在这个夏末秋初 遇见成都...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":382,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财摄记","slug":"西财摄记","count":9,"path":"api/categories/西财摄记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"夏","slug":"夏","count":6,"path":"api/tags/夏.json"}],"author":{"name":"Swufe了吗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/deelsilcon/pics/raw/master/uPic/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"分享生活，记录美好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"weichat":{"icon":"/img/wechat.png","link":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303234741533.png"},"mail":{"icon":"/img/mail.png","link":"mailto:271215314@qq.com"}}}}},"next_post":{"title":"西财摄记| 西瓜味的清凉夏日","uid":"9b0944fb16880cfc8ee986c5b61366e4","slug":"推文5","date":"2021-07-19T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T16:19:01.431Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文5.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225943513.png","text":"序 你是一种感觉， 写在夏日晚风里。 盛夏的光夏天的光，为成都增添了许多浪漫气息。 和许多人一样，我在上课途中，也常常流连于难得一见的蓝天白云。 一直想拍一组宫崎骏夏天味道的写真，可惜校内没有十分合适的地点。 想起平常散步经常去的鲁家滩，清凉又治愈。挑了个阳光明媚的下午，就和静宝...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":428,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财摄记","slug":"西财摄记","count":9,"path":"api/categories/西财摄记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"夏","slug":"夏","count":6,"path":"api/tags/夏.json"}],"author":{"name":"Swufe了吗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/deelsilcon/pics/raw/master/uPic/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"分享生活，记录美好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"weichat":{"icon":"/img